3</a>]\n\n<b>4. 레버리지 ETF 규제 논란</b>\n김용범 금융위원회 부위원장은 단일 종목 레버리지 ETF의 상장 폐지는 시장에 엄청난 충격을 줄 수 있어 어렵다는 입장을 밝혔습니다. [<a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMib0FVX3lxTE5OVHcxRlFfZWQ2Y1Jlb3c4c0dlNDRpaGFqV0tyQW92dW9ndjhaVFpEbExFR1dPNDJ4UXJJaVRocUpiTGF2aTY1V2JsSDY5Z0lpbDJXRUhOcXdZS2Y5Wk9ZUUoyZTlraGRKd0hSck1naw?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#6</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiiAFBVV95cUxNUDY3TDY3amdjVVQtcWhMRWhXQUc4M1NfYW5CTWRpSkxFWlRBT3lIdG5DeGwxVWZzOW5JMEhBU3ZxQnZDUnlWWmNMcFR6TTBDSzdTWlhnWkh6MU84dURvalpiZllvelZGOXEyWWI1aHBoUFQwS3BiMEdqMEtpMk1WSTN5ZVY0WXB4?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#7</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiY0FVX3lxTFA3cmR6X2phSm1OTUJvQ1JYcUIyYlA3R1dRT1BYYk93UUtwMThjSzcxaVZpYl9rRnZJYUw1ZjZxY3BNWWFzYy1HNjFvcjRFOVdSMzRqeGpkTmtudkQxc3p5TTQxSQ?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#17</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiRkFVX3lxTFA2NjVaMnNhZ2hlWGw3dnFKdmNjTi1CWXlXTktrM0d2WDVFWkxNeHQxVmcwQW1wdzVKaUE3WHAySGN1SmdEc0E?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#19</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#20</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiRkFVX3lxTE9yYlNyZ2NiY2lfOVVTd1YxWGJZeDdnUUh6d3J6OEFSQnE3ZE5ZQTRHUThIZVZQcklhY29qWHB1alZ2Y2IyMmc?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#22</a>] 이는 국내 증시에서 레버리지 ETF가 개인 투자자들에게 큰 영향을 미치고 있는 상황에서, 규제 당국이 시장 안정성을 우선시하는 모습을 보여줍니다. [<a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiWkFVX3lxTE9hS2toemxCc1dGMmFJMWdBRUpHTklzdEFYSnhFRGxmVmFHZUFicWNMRXo3M0hVV2V4QllYRF9mNmNnbGFCM2hxb2ZSMVZ2TEJNNnlFdWEwMUowUdIBVEFVX3lxTE10RDNabHdtMkdaUHNBTVNqcV8waUNHcnVka1ZFNWM2WGJGSUhyZTVGV0phSDZOc1JNX3NveEp0OXRkOFNDQXB4YmJsbTF1TWllR1dBUQ?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#10</a>]", "brief_at": "2026-07-20 01:35", "premium": [{"t": "07-19 10:57", "title": "덕평보다 큰 쿠팡32센터 화재, 손실·책임 셈법은", "link": "https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiiAFBVV95cUxOTXQ4QVJRaEp1R0l6alhOakdzV1FIZG1wTXBmZlB6d3pDTTls